::Grounded::
Grounded's heart stops as the knifes fly at Trinity. After seeing her 
jump them he gets inraged. He runs at Deemos putting away his pistol and 
his energon whips flying to his hands.  The green whips of pure energy 
flow out of the handles.  He whips one at Deemos legs ttrying to wrap it 
and one at his neck with the same intent.  The enery in the whips is so 
concentrated that it burns on touch.
